title: The Smiths - Complete Discography (Apple Lossless)
description:
The Smiths&#039; Complete discography, ripped from master CDs from my cousin&#039;s collection.  She has almost all of the Smiths&#039; CDs, and would highly disapprove of my putting them up here for you to enjoy.  :)

I am hoping that some kid downloads this and discovers the Smiths, and loves them as much as I did when I was 16.


Included:

Ask (single)
Best Of 1
Hatful Of Hollow
Interview Picture Disc
Louder Than Bombs
Meat Is Murder
The Queen Is Dead
Rank (live)
Self-Titled
Strangeways, Here We Come
Sweet And Tender Hooligan (single)

Any single, live, or b-side FLAC or Apple Lossless additions would be greatly appreciated!!!

Keep adding to the collection, as long as it is lossless audio!

Have fun.
